** IF YOU USE THIS PACKAGE - DON'T FORGET TO GIVE IT A CHEEKY HIGH FIVE **
Fugue icon pack for Umbraco - This version, just like the famfamfam icons is not using sprites so you may notice performance issues if you have your browser cache disabled, but you'll have loads of cool icons to choose from :)
There are over 2300 icons to choose from, and I did trim some out to try and reduce the amount of icons but gave up in the end.
These icons are freely available from http://p.yusukekamiyamane.com/ and are created by Yusuke Kamiyamane, so feel free to give him a big 'High Five You Rock' on his site or on twitter http://twitter.com/ykamiyamane Once Shannon has sprite'd the famfamfam icon package, I'll ripoff steal take a look at how he has done it and apply it to this package :P
//==== Remove Unwanted Icons ====//
You can easily remove unwanted icons yourself, just open the following folder in your Umbraco install and delete
/umbraco/images/umbraco
This will help keep performance of the icon dropdown and make it easier to pick a good one
